{"tid":1520323,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"你班中學雞入黎！！！開學啦就黎","createTime":"2019-08-30T18:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T05:47:25.000Z","uid":35190,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a69ea5c08c14e8556e6fc407faca8705f96dccfd","tid":1520323,"uid":35190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T18:10:13.000Z","msg":"就黎開學，對於罷唔罷課較大爭議應在中學，<br />\n大學本身自由度較大；小學應該家長都唔放心。<br />\n<br />\n無論您地取態點都好，作為老師，小小建議：<br />\n<br />\n1. 任何時間以自身安全為最大原則，如以多人小組、如果本身體格瘦弱真係唔好上咁前（12、3歲中學雞真心未必要上咁前.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n2. 重點！返到學校，梗係有老師社工關愛下您做咩～～～拿！任何發夢經歷都唔使如實交代，例如日期啦、地點啦、衣著啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如有有信任既老師，可以分享下情緒既惱惱，你有我有大家都有，但發夢既野就忘記啦。如果您講左，唔排除會記低再sd比教育局，之後自己諗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 再補充。"},{"pid":"bac0e888d9cb5a4cba71d693165262cba843fd5e","tid":1520323,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T18:10:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dyrx7H5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyrx7H5.gif&h=f7c0f28c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2VYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=514b7e8c\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2VYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=384b2b20\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2VYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAf